  Lun7 siat bok8-chu2 kap che3 bok8-chu2 e5 m7-tioh8. TaN kou2-cha2 lang5 siat bok8-chu2 che3-su7, sui-bong2 si7 beh hou7 lang5 ki3-liam7, iau2-ku2 iah8 si7 m7-tioh8. In-ui7 che3-su7 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 siat, hou7 lang5 tit-tioh8 thang hian3-che3 lai5 siok8 choe7. Lang5 chi2-u7 thang che3 ti7 Siong7-te3; na7 eng7 chit-e5 le2-sou3 khi3 che3 thiN-toe7, kui2-sin5, bok8-chu2, che si7 chhiam3-koan5 lam7-sam2, put-chi2 tek-choe7 Siong7-te3. Koh iah8 si7 hoan7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 kai3-lut8; Siong7-te3 e5 kai3 kong2, “Goa2 i2- goa7, m7-thang u7 pat8-e5 Siong7-te3; bok8-tit tiau-khek ngou2-siong7.” Lang5 chhai7 bok8- chu2, si7 hoan7-tioh8 chit-e5 kai3. M7-tan7-na7 an2-ni, iah8 si7 hoan7-tioh8 Tiong-kok e5 kou2- le2. Chiau3 Tiong-kok e5 kou2-le2, tok8-tok8 tioh8 Hong5-te3 kap chu-hou5 chiah oe7 chhai7-tit bok8-chu2, peh-siN3-lang5 long2 boe7 tit-thang chhai7 bok8-chu2, iah8 boe7 tit- thang khi2 chou2-bio7. Koh Hong5-te3 chiah oe7 che3 tit chhit-tai7 e5 chou2, chu-hou5 oe7 che3 tit gou7-tai7 e5 chou2; peh-siN3 chi2-u7 oe7 tit-thang che3 i e5 pe7-bu2 tiaN7-tiaN7. 
  Kau3 Beng5-tiau5 chiah koh tiaN7-tioh8 peh-siN3 iah8 oe7 tit-thang che3 kau3 saN-tai7 e5 chou2, na7-si7 chit-tiap8 e5 peh-siN3-lang5, chhiam3-koan5 khi2 chou2-bio7, chhai7 bok8-chu2, che3 kau3 kui2 chap8 tai7; che m7-tan7-na7 si7 bo5 chiau3 to7-li2, iah8 si7 bo5 chiau3 le2-sou3. Koh lang5 chhai7 bok8-chu2, hoan2-tng2 si7 siat-tok8--tioh8 chou2-kong tiaN7-tiaN7. In-ui7 bok8-chu2 si7 chha5-pang, kap-choh-tiam3 sou2 eng7 chhiu2 siN--e5; lang5 chiong kui2-e5 chiN5 chhin3-chhai2 khi3 boe2 chit8-sian lai5, chiu7 ho7-choe3 lan2 e5 chou2-kong. Siat-su2 chou2-kong oe7 chai, kiam2 m7 put-chi2 toa7 siu7- khi3 mah? ChhiaN2 eng7 phi3-ju7 lai5 kong2. Cheng-siN pi2 chhiu7-bak8 si7 khah kui3-khi3; lang5 liah8 cheng-siN choe3 lan2 e5 chou2-kong, chiu7 lan2 tek-khak toa7 siu7-khi3; iah8 lan2 ka-ki7 liah8 chha5-pang choe3 lan2 e5 chou2-kong, m7-chai-kio3 si7 leng5-jiok8 chou2-kong, che-si7 toa7 chho3-gou7. Cha2 u7 chit8-chiah Tai7-Eng kok e5 chun5 khi3 In3-tou7 kok, chhau3-tu2-kham2 u7 chit8-chiah chiau2 pe lai5, hioh ti7 ui5 teng2; chun5-chu2 bong2 eng7 chheng3 ka7 i phah--si2. Liam5-piN In3- tou7 e5 lang5 long2 ui5-lui5 lai5, m7 pang3 i soah. Chun5-chu2 mng7 si7 siaN2-su7; hia-e5 lang5 in3 kong2, “Li2 tiN3 m7-chai, li2 tu2-a2 phah-si2 e5 chiau2 si7 goan2 e5 chou2-kong.” Chun5-chu2 iah8 kiaN, iah8 ho2 chhio3; chiah siuN7 chit8-e5 ke3 ka2-chia3 kong2, “Na7-si7 an2-ni, chiu7 goa2 bo5 m7-tioh8; goa2 ti7 goan2 kok nih8, goan2 chou2 si2, khi3 piN3 choe3 hi5, khit lin2 e5 chou2 teh khi3 chiah8. Sou2-i2 goa2 jip8 kau3 chia, thoe3-goan2 chou2 po3 siu5; an2-ni, lin2 chou2 chiah8 goan2 e5 chou2, goa2 phah si2 lin2 e5 chou2, kiam2 m7 hap8-gi5 mah?” Hia-e5 lang5 bo5 oe7 thang in3, chiah khi3. TaN m7-chai Tiong- kok lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit-e5 tai7-chi3, phah- sng3 In3-tou7 lang5 si7 tioh8 a2 m7-tioh8. Goa2 phah-sng3 tak8-lang5 long2 si7 chhio3 i cho3 gong7, na7-si7 i sui-bong2 si7 gong7, iau2-ku2 si7 liah8 oah8 chiau2 choe3 i e5 chou2-kong; iah8 lan2 koh si7 liah8 si2-si2 e5 chhiu7-chha5 lai5 ch